vdr (1.7.22-0yavdr0~oneiric) oneiric; urgency=medium
  
  [Tobi]
  * New upstream release
  * Dropped 99_dvbc-unitiymedia-fix.dpatch - fixed upstream
  * Dropped multipatch patches - these are available in the etobi-branch
    of the Git repository
  * Updated opt-39_noepg.dpatch and opt-44_rotor.dpatch
  * Upgraded opt-20_liemikuutio.dpatch to version 1.33
  * Dropped dpatch and use quilt for the patches - no PATCHVARIANT support
    anymore! To build VDR with a different set of patches, grab the
    appropriate branch from the Git.
  * Dropped reelchannelscan patch
  * Added build-arch, build-indep targets
  * Added installation of the dvbhddevice plugin
  * chown +r on /proc/av7110_ir and /proc/budget_ci_ir
  * Standards-Version: 3.9.2
  * Use 3.0 source formate and bz2 tarballs
  * Reordered debian/vdr.install
  * Dropped extensions patch
  * Updated commands.ctvdr.conf to new upstream format
  [yaVDR]
  * install scr.conf -> etc/vdr/ (unicable)
  * Added opt-54_x_pin.patch
  * Added opt-55_wareagleicon.patch
  * Added opt-56_eventdetails_v3.patch
  * Added opt-57_vdr-remote_instant_recordings.patch
  * Added opt-58_dvbplayer-no-busy.patch
  * Added opt-59_hd-timeshift-wait.patch
  * Added opt-60-livebuffer12-rmm.patch
  * Updated opt-42-x_MainMenuHooks.patch -> v.1.0.1
  * Added opt-61_dynamite.patch
  * Added opt-62_hard_link_cutter.patch
  * Added opt-99_vdr-hotfixes.patch
  * Added opt-63_naludump.patch
  * Added opt-64_dvbt2-support.patch
  * Removed sortrec.patch

 -- Holger Schvestka <email address hidden>  Fri, 23 Dec 2011 14:30:04 +0200

